title: The Wilson Burgundy
body_html: Reimagining the classic loafer, the Wilson is a modern and stylish slip-on with both comfort and personality. Featuring a unique and thoughtful design and made in Brush Off Krumenauer leather in Burgundy, the Wilson is Blake Rapid Stitched and is constructed on our new Denver sole for comfort and traction. Dressed up or down, with socks or no socks, the Wilson is the update to a classic design that your closet has been needing.

title: The Lou Tobacco
body_html: Designed with elements of several classic styles in mind, the Lou is a fresh and versatile boot that can compliment any man's wardrobe. Made of soft, water resistant Rusan suede and featuring HELM's slip-resistant rubber cushion sole, the Lou is immediately comfortable and ready for wherever the road takes you. Also available in Black, Brown and Teak.

title: The Charlie Navy
body_html: The first of its kind at HELM, the Charlie is a sleek and stylish hybrid of a sneaker and a boot. Made of soft Krumenauer leather and featuring an extra padded shaft and tongue, the Charlie is instantly comfortable out of the box. Featuring a rubber cupsole, popular d-ring hardware and two speed hooks, the Charlie is sporty and ready to take you anywhere your day leads.

title: The Xander Navy
body_html: The Xander is designed with minimalist and modern aesthetics in mind, creating a versatile sneaker that can be dressed up or down. Constructed with Krumenauer leather and the customer favorite cup sole, the Xander is both beautiful and comfortable and perfect for any adventure, both day and night.

title: The Hynes Brown
body_html: The Hynes is an updated Chukka boot, both stylish and comfortable with modern elements for today's man. Made in the softest leather we have ever used, Neymar, as well as a padded collar around the ankle, the Hynes is instantly comfortable and requires little to no break-in period. The Hynes also features a new custom sole designed by HELM, with a poured rubber outsole and stacked leather heel for comfort and exceptional longevity.

title: The Hollis Olive
body_html: The ruggedness of the Marion meets the refinement of the Zind, the Hollis is a boot perfect to complement any wardrobe. Made of supple full-grain Babbo leather, it’s a work-boot style and dress boot combined to create a class of its own. The Mini-Lug sole offers traction and stability while still keeping a slimmer profile. The 415 last gives it a more narrow form while the double and triple stitch throughout make it a style versatile enough to accompany all of your outfits.

title: The Knox Natural
body_html: The Knox is a contemporary blend of our customer favorites, the Pablo and The Charlie. Blending the pattern of an Italian moto boot with the cupsole from our Charlie sneaker, the Knox is both casual and sleek at the same time. Replacing laces with a YKK zipper adds a distinct style as well as ease of getting on and off. Dress it up, dress it down, the Knox is ready for however you choose to wear it.

title: High Shine Wax Polish by Pure Polish
body_html:
​Used for protecting and shining non-suede/non-patent leather goods, typically toe caps and heel quarters of dress shoes. This is our recommended polish for adding a mirror shine (bull shine or spit shine) The High Shine Paste Polish has no color; it's a non-pigmented, clear polish. Perfect if you don't want to worry about color-matching, or for vintage or dress shoes with a patina.

- 2 oz

- Made of cold-pressed orange oil, carnauba wax, white beeswax

title: Cream Polish by Pure Polish
body_html:
Use for protecting, conditioning, and shining all non-suede/non-patent leather goods. The Color Cream Polish is a pigmented/colored polish. This is our "everyday" polish. Perfect if you want to restore color, condition, and add a soft shine to any of your leather goods.

- 2 oz.

- Made of cold-pressed orange oil, yellow beeswax, carnauba wax, cold-pressed coconut oil, non-toxic pigments

title: HELM Boot Care Kit
body_html:
Custom made of Horween leather, the HELM Boot Care Kit includes the essentials to keep your boots looking their best. A perfect size for travel, this kit can go wherever your boots take you. The kit includes:

  • Blackrock Leather 'n Rich
  • Shoe Shine Brush
  • Polishing Cloth
  • Available in Black Chromexcel, Brown Chromexcel, and Burgundy Color 8 Chromexcel

title: Blackrock Leather 'n Rich
body_html:
BLACKROCK has a unique formulation that is colorless to enhance all leather tones, is easy to use, and economical.  

The genuine carnauba wax wipes easily to a shine.  Cleans, nourishes, beautifies all finished leather, all colors to a rich mellow glow.  Will not change color or shade of leather.  

Best On: All finished leathers, exotic leathers, any color.  Not for use on suede or Nubuck.  

Made In America

Net Weight: 4 ounces

title: The Emmett Whiskey
body_html:
The Emmett is made to order and may take up to 5 business days to ship.

This product is not available for discounts or promotions.

 

Durable enough to take you all over town and comfortable enough to wear around the house, the Emmett is 3D printed in flexible, responsive TPU with an upper handcrafted in supple Krumenauer leather, a HELM staple. The construction and materials are specially selected with the intent of recycling every component for a second life.
The Collaboration of HELM & HILOS
HELM by HILOS grew out of a shared commitment to the way things get made. HILOS designs for a circular future, building technology for the future of footwear. Every pair of HELM is designed for comfort, longevity and timeless appeal. Together, we believe leaving a lighter footprint makes a major impact.

title: The Jakob Brown
body_html: In 2018, we released the original Jakob, and it quickly sold out and became a customer favorite. Through the years, we've received many emails and phone calls asking us to bring it back, and now in 2021, it's finally here. The new Jakob is inspired by a traditional work boot, but with a tapered toe and elegant details. Featuring the tallest profile of any boot we make, the Jakob is both sturdy and lightweight. Constructed in full gain Krumenauer leather and our HELM branded rubber cushion sole, the Jakob offers all-day comfort for anywhere your day takes you.

title: The Death & Co. Jakob Black
body_html:
Death & Co. is an epic cocktail institution, rooted in award winning recipes, exceptional service, and unparalleled hospitality. With current locations in New York City, Denver, and Los Angeles, Death & Co. is revolutionizing the art of service. We are proud to offer this limited edition style in collaboration with the Death & Co. Team. 

In 2018, we released the original Jakob, and it quickly sold out and became a customer favorite. Through the years, we've received many emails and phone calls asking us to bring it back, and now in 2021, it's finally here. The new Jakob is inspired by a traditional work boot, but with a tapered toe and elegant details. Featuring the tallest profile of any boot we make, the Jakob is both sturdy and lightweight. Constructed in full gain Krumenauer leather and our HELM branded rubber cushion sole, the Jakob offers all-day comfort for anywhere your day takes you.

title: HELM Socks - Black+Grey
body_html:
Designed by HELM and made in North Carolina, these socks are made for comfort and longevity, just like your HELM boots and shoes. Made of the best materials we could find and designed with added cushion in the footbed, HELM socks are the perfect daily complement to your HELM footwear. 

  • 36% Recycled Cotton, 33% Recycled Polyester, 27% Nylon, 4% Spandex
  • Constructed with extra cushion in the footbed for added comfort
  • Fits men's sizes 7-13
  • Made in the U.S.A.
